tion between sensors and motor systems. Here, we demonstrate first evidence for the existence of congruent maps of sensory space in the bat SC that might serve to generate a unified representation of the environment to guide motor actions.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Hoffmann, Susanne", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Vega\u2010Zuniga, Tomas", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Greiter, Wolfgang", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Krabichler, Quirin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bley, Alexandra", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Matthes, Mariana", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zimmer, Christiane", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Firzlaff, Uwe", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Luksch, Harald", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Foxe, John", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/476bb774dae2848eb7414899dfcb9e5d", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/c5b839ecaa15269781e7fc82bc6ee7a33988f48e28dcbced5d4e30b5dfd40c1d", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/NX3ZGPDF", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/NX3ZGPDF", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/187bbc4671b80c3ebe96f2aecabe0f75!/b226062-228532", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "9", 